    "Strip away the residency benefits. The pure investment fundamentals — 4–7% net yield, 10–15% annual appreciation, and EU asset domicile — make Greek property one of the most compelling yield-plus-growth plays in Europe right now.": "Strip away the residency benefits. The pure investment fundamentals — 4–7% net yield, 10–15% annual appreciation, and EU asset domicile — make Greek property one of the most compelling yield-plus-growth plays in Europe right now.",
