    "Dubai's Golden Visa, while genuinely useful for tax optimization and business purposes, provides none of this. A UAE residency is issued by the UAE government and can be revoked or restricted. It provides no Schengen travel rights. It has no citizenship pathway. It places you in a jurisdiction that, while internally stable, is surrounded by active conflict zones and sits outside the world's most powerful security alliance.": "迪拜的 Golden Visa 虽然对于税收优化和商业目的确实有用，但并没有提供这些。 UAE 居留权由 UAE 政府颁发，可以撤销或限制。它不提供 Schengen 旅行权利。它没有公民途径。它使您所处的司法管辖区虽然内部稳定，但周围都是活跃的冲突地区，并且位于世界上最强大的安全联盟之外。",
