    "Floor Plan": "平面图",
    "For families from the Middle East, Southeast Asia, or countries with restricted passport mobility, this is transformative. Children can enroll in Greek international schools and EU universities with EU-resident tuition rates. Elderly parents gain access to Greece's EU-quality healthcare system. The entire family gains Schengen travel freedom with one investment.": "对于来自中东、东南亚或护照流动性受限国家的家庭来说，这是变革性的。儿童可以以 EU 居民学费入读希腊国际学校和 EU 大学。年迈的父母可以享受希腊的 EU 优质医疗保健系统。通过一项投资，整个家庭即可获得 Schengen 旅行自由。",
    "For HNW investors with a diversification mandate, Greek real estate at the €800K level provides: EU hard asset domicile, no annual wealth tax, path to the €100K non-dom tax regime with proper structuring, Schengen freedom for the entire family, and a hard asset with growing institutional buy-side interest that supports future liquidity.": "对于具有多元化授权的高净值投资者来说，80万欧元水平的希腊房地产提供：EU硬资产住所、免年度财富税、通过适当的结构实现10万欧元非本地税制的途径、整个家庭的Schengen自由度以及机构买方兴趣不断增长的硬资产，以支持未来的流动性。",
    "For investors seeking lifestyle and yield, the Athenian Riviera is the sweet spot: close enough to Athens for city access, coastal enough for premium holiday rentals, and undervalued enough that capital appreciation remains a credible outcome over a 5–7 year hold.": "对于寻求生活方式和收益的投资者来说，雅典里维埃拉是最佳地点：距离雅典足够近，可以进入城市，沿海足够大，可以提供优质的度假租赁，而且估值足够低，资本增值在持有 5-7 年期间仍然是一个可靠的结果。",
    "for off-market listings.": "用于场外上市。",
    "Four Investment Pillars of Greek Property": "希腊房地产的四大投资支柱",
    "Four Tax Advantages of Greek Residency": "希腊居留权的四大税收优势",
    "Frequently Asked Questions": "常见问题解答",
    "From a portfolio construction perspective, Greek real estate offers genuine diversification. It has low correlation with US and Northern European equity markets, demonstrates resilience during global rate cycles (it bottomed before rates peaked), and benefits from tourism tailwinds that are structurally unrelated to financial market volatility.": "从投资组合构建的角度来看，希腊房地产提供了真正的多元化。它与美国和北欧股市的相关性较低，在全球利率周期中表现出弹性（在利率见顶之前触底），并受益于与金融市场波动在结构上无关的旅游业顺风。",
    "From consultation to visa approval with full support.": "从咨询到签证审批全程支持。",
    "From Faliro to Vouliagmeni, the Athenian Riviera represents 30km of coastline with direct access to Athens city centre. Properties here command some of the highest short-term rental rates in Greece — €150–€350 per night in peak season — yet purchase prices remain 40–60% below comparable Mediterranean markets like Barcelona, Nice, or the Amalfi Coast.": "从法利罗 (Faliro) 到沃立歌美尼 (Vouliagmeni)，雅典里维埃拉 (Athenian Riviera) 海岸线长达 30 公里，可直达雅典市中心。这里的房产拥有希腊最高的短期租金——旺季每晚 150 至 350 欧元——但购买价格仍比巴塞罗那、尼斯或阿马尔菲海岸等地中海市场低 40 至 60%。",
    "From First Call to": "从第一次通话到",
