    "Hand-picked, pre-verified properties in Athens, Piraeus, Glyfada, and the Athenian Riviera — each qualifying for the": "雅典、比雷埃夫斯、吉利法达和雅典里维埃拉精心挑选、预先验证的房产——每处房产都有资格获得",
