    "Mail Us": "给我们发邮件",
    "Many residency-by-investment programs advertise 'family inclusion' but restrict the rights granted to dependents or charge per-capita fees. The Greek Golden Visa works differently. Each family member receives their own biometric residency card with full rights — including the right to live, study, and work anywhere in Greece, and to travel visa-free across the entire 27-country Schengen Area.": "许多投资居留计划宣传“家庭包容”，但限制授予家属的权利或按人均收费。希腊语 Golden Visa 的工作方式有所不同。每个家庭成员都会收到自己的生物识别居留卡，并享有全部权利，包括在希腊任何地方生活、学习和工作的权利，以及在整个 27 个国家/地区的 Schengen 地区免签证旅行的权利。",
    "MENA investors are rethinking their residency strategy. Against a backdrop of regional instability, the comparison between EU safety and Gulf exposure has never been more relevant. Here's the honest analysis.": "MENA 投资者正在重新考虑他们的居住策略。在地区不稳定的背景下，EU 安全性和海湾风险之间的比较从未如此相关。这是诚实的分析。",
    "MENA Security Context — 2025": "MENA 安全环境 — 2025",
    "Month 1–2": "第 1-2 个月",
