    "Month 4–8": "第 4-8 个月",
    "months end-to-end": "几个月的端到端",
    "More Guides": "更多指南",
    "Most Golden Visa investors think of their property as a cost centre — a €250,000 commitment that secures residency but generates no return. The reality for well-selected properties in Athens and the Athenian Riviera is the opposite. Athens became one of Europe's fastest-growing short-term rental markets. Tourism arrivals hit a record 35 million in 2023 and continued climbing in 2024.": "大多数 Golden Visa 投资者将他们的房产视为成本中心——投入 250,000 欧元即可获得居住权，但不会产生任何回报。雅典和雅典里维埃拉精心挑选的房产的实际情况却恰恰相反。雅典成为欧洲增长最快的短期租赁市场之一。 2023 年，旅游人数达到创纪录的 3500 万人次，并在 2024 年继续攀升。",
    "Most investors track yields. The smart ones track what €250,000 actually buys: EU residency, Schengen freedom, a coastal home on the Mediterranean, and an entirely different quality of life.": "大多数投资者都会追踪收益率。聪明人会追踪 25 万欧元实际购买的东西：EU 居住权、Schengen 自由、地中海沿海住宅以及完全不同的生活质量。",
