    "Note:": "笔记：",
    "One conversation with our advisors will give you a complete family application roadmap — timeline, costs, and property shortlist tailored to your family size.": "与我们的顾问进行一次对话，将为您提供一份完整的家庭申请路线图——根据您的家庭规模量身定制的时间表、费用和财产候选名单。",
    "One fee. No hidden charges. Our advisory covers the complete journey — from first call to ongoing rental management after your permit is issued.": "一笔费用。无隐藏费用。我们的咨询涵盖整个过程——从第一次致电到您获得许可证后的持续租赁管理。",
    "One frequently overlooked compliance item: the Short-Term Rental (STR) registration. If you intend to rent your property on Airbnb or Booking.com, you must register with the Greek Ministry of Tourism's MHTE system and obtain a registration number, which is displayed on all listings. Failure to register can result in fines of up to €50,000. Our properties come with existing or ready-to-activate MHTE registration as part of the handover package.": "一项经常被忽视的合规项目：短期租赁 (STR) 注册。如果您打算在 Airbnb 或 Booking.com 上出租您的房产，您必须在希腊旅游部的 MHTE 系统中注册并获取注册号，该注册号将显示在所有列表中。未能注册可能会导致高达 50,000 欧元的罚款。我们的房产附带现有或准备激活的 MHTE 注册，作为移交包的一部分。",
    "One Investment.": "一项投资。",
    "Our advisors handle the entire process — from property selection to permit issuance. Start with a free 20-minute call.": "我们的顾问负责处理整个过程——从房产选择到许可证颁发。从 20 分钟的免费通话开始。",
    "Our advisors handle the entire process — from property selection to permit issuance. Talk to us today.": "我们的顾问负责处理整个过程——从房产选择到许可证颁发。今天和我们谈谈。",
    "Our advisors have guided investors from 40+ countries through the Greek program. Get your personalised analysis in 24 hours.": "我们的顾问已指导来自 40 多个国家的投资者完成希腊计划。 24 小时内获得您的个性化分析。",
    "Our advisors work alongside qualified Greek tax attorneys to structure each investment for optimal outcome. Speak with us before you invest.": "我们的顾问与合格的希腊税务律师合作，设计每项投资以获得最佳结果。投资前请先与我们联系。",
    "Our team sources off-market opportunities tailored to your budget and timeline.": "我们的团队会根据您的预算和时间表寻找场外机会。",
    "Permits are issued for 5 years and renewed simultaneously for the entire family as long as the qualifying property is maintained. There is no requirement for family members to be physically present in Greece during renewal — the process can be handled through the same power-of-attorney framework used for the original application.": "许可证有效期为 5 年，只要保留合格财产，整个家庭即可同时续签。续签期间不需要家庭成员亲自在希腊 - 该过程可以通过与原始申请相同的授权书框架来处理。",
    "Plan My Family Application": "计划我的家庭申请",
    "Portugal retains one clear advantage: citizenship timeline. At 5 years versus 7 for Greece, it is faster for investors who view a European passport as their primary goal. For investors seeking real estate yield, capital appreciation, and EU residency at the lowest entry point — Greece is the 2025 winner.": "葡萄牙保留了一项明显的优势：公民身份时间表。希腊的期限为 5 年，而希腊的期限为 7 年，对于以欧洲护照为主要目标的投资者来说，期限更快。对于寻求最低切入点的房地产收益率、资本增值和 EU 居住权的投资者来说，希腊是 2025 年的赢家。",
    "Portugal's Golden Visa program was the benchmark between 2012 and 2022, attracting over €7 billion in real estate investment. Then the government began restricting qualifying property types — first removing Lisbon and Porto, then expanding exclusions to coastal zones. By 2023, residential property in Portugal's most desirable locations no longer qualified. Investors were pushed toward investment funds, heritage projects, and rural properties — assets with different risk and liquidity profiles.": "葡萄牙的 Golden Visa 计划是 2012 年至 2022 年间的基准，吸引了超过 70 亿欧元的房地产投资。然后政府开始限制符合条件的房产类型——首先取消里斯本和波尔图，然后将排除范围扩大到沿海地区。到 2023 年，葡萄牙最理想地点的住宅物业不再符合资格。投资者被推向投资基金、遗产项目和农村财产——具有不同风险和流动性状况的资产。",
    "Pre-renovated, Golden Visa eligible, and managed for income from day one.": "预先装修，符合 Golden Visa 资格，并从第一天起就开始管理收入。",
    "Pre-verified Golden Visa properties with full compliance — analyze and compare independently.": "预先验证的 Golden Visa 属性完全符合要求 — 独立分析和比较。",
    "Pre-verified Golden Visa properties with full compliance — analyze and compare independently. All properties qualify for the Greek Golden Visa program.": "预先验证的 Golden Visa 属性完全符合要求 — 独立分析和比较。所有房产均符合希腊 Golden Visa 计划的资格。",
    "Pre-Verified Investment Properties": "预先验证的投资物业",
    "Pre-verified investment properties starting at €250,000.": "预先验证的投资房产起价为 250,000 欧元。",
