    "properties I found for you! Tap one to learn more, or skip to continue.": "我为你找到的房产！点击其中一项以了解更多信息，或跳过以继续。",
    "Properties in high-demand zones (central Athens, Thessaloniki, Mykonos, Santorini) require the €400,000 threshold. Always confirm zoning with your legal advisor before purchase.": "高需求地区（雅典市中心、塞萨洛尼基、米科诺斯岛、圣托里尼岛）的房产需要 40 万欧元的门槛。购买前请务必与您的法律顾问确认分区。",
