    "Get Started": "התחל",
    "Golden Visa": "Golden Visa",
    "Golden Visa Eligible Properties": "Golden Visa נכסים כשירים",
    "Golden Visa in Greece": "Golden Visa ביוון",
    "Golden Visa Journey?": "Golden Visa מסע?",
    "Golden Visa Permit": "Golden Visa היתר",
    "Golden Visa Properties": "Golden Visa מאפיינים",
